# Vercel Deployment Configuration

# Frontend Environment Variables
# Add these in Vercel Dashboard → Your Project → Settings → Environment Variables

## Required
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://YOUR_EC2_PUBLIC_IP:5000/api/v1

# After setting up custom domain with HTTPS:
# NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://api.yourdomain.com/api/v1

## Notes:
# - Replace YOUR_EC2_PUBLIC_IP with your actual EC2 public IP address
# - Or use your custom API domain if you've set up DNS + SSL
# - The backend routes are mounted at /api/v1 in the Express app
# - This variable is used by frontend/lib/api.ts for all API calls
